<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>醫院平均用量 - Xolair MMP</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { user }) %>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="layout-2col">
      <div>
        <div class="toolbar">
          <input type="text" id="searchBox" placeholder="搜尋醫院名稱...">
        </div>
        <div id="hospitalList"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="card" id="formCard" style="display:none;">
          <h2 id="formTitle" style="margin-top:0;"></h2>
          <div style="color:#6b7684; font-size:0.85rem; margin-bottom:1rem;" id="formSubtitle"></div>
          <form id="usageForm">
            <div class="form-grid">
              <div class="field"><label>2026年1月用量</label><input type="number" name="usage_2026_01" step="0.01" class="calc-input"></div>
              <div class="field"><label>2026年2月用量</label><input type="number" name="usage_2026_02" step="0.01" class="calc-input"></div>
              <div class="field"><label>2026年3月用量</label><input type="number" name="usage_2026_03" step="0.01" class="calc-input"></div>
              <div class="field"><label>2026年4月用量</label><input type="number" name="usage_2026_04" step="0.01" class="calc-input"></div>
              <div class="field"><label>2026年5月用量</label><input type="number" name="usage_2026_05" step="0.01" class="calc-input"></div>
              <div class="field"><label>2026年6月用量</label><input type="number" name="usage_2026_06" step="0.01" class="calc-input"></div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>平均用量</label>
                <input type="number" name="average_usage" step="0.01">
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>已填月份平均（參考，非必填依據）</label>
                <input type="text" id="autoAvgDisplay" class="readonly-field" readonly>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:1rem;">
              <button type="submit">儲存</button>
              <span class="save-status" id="saveStatus"></span>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="card" id="emptyState">
          <p style="color:#6b7684;">請從左側選擇一間醫院以填寫 2026 年 1~6 月用量與平均用量。若某個月沒有問到資料可以留空，平均用量請自行填寫。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/hospital-usage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
